        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe tpl function was introduced in helm 2.5. You probably have version 2.3 coming OOB with rancher. However, rancher documentation says that helm can be updated to later version: http://rancher.com/docs/rancher/latest/en/kubernetes/addons/#upgrading-helm",
